creator: Intellum Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Retail Training from Google. It’s a faster, smarter way to learn with great classes and quizzes to help turn you into a Google pro. Even better? You’ll earn points for completing each of them — and points mean prizes. Everyone loves prizes.

It’s designed to let you learn what you want, how you want, when you want. You’ll master products — from top features and customer profiles, through to fun demo tips — in 5 minutes, and get access to the latest training the moment it’s out.

So, are you ready to start learning? Then let’s go!
descriptionShort: The fastest, smartest way to become a Google product pro.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Hello all learners, we are continuously adding new features, fixing bugs, and improving app performance. In this update we’ve fixed menu items.
